section.section:
The failure of a person to use a seat belt or restraining device required under this section may not:
Be considered evidence of negligence;
Be considered evidence of contributory negligence;
Limit liability of a party or an insurer;
Diminish recovery for damages arising out of the ownership, maintenance, or operation of a motor vehicle; or
Be considered a moving violation for purposes of § 16-402 of this article.
